"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Hope you all had a nice Christmas. We continue with another testnet (a short and easy one this time).\\n\\n[Bridge Network](https://twitter.com/bridgenetwork0x) is a decentralized hub with multiple cross-chain tools such as token bridge, NFT bridge and cross-chain liquidity aggregator. It also enables token issuers to deploy a bridge for their token easily.\\n\\nBridge Network is now having an airdrop program for their testnet users. Everyone who participates will receive BRG tokens. The airdrop program ends on 22nd January 2022.\\n\\n**Getting Started:**\\n\\nBridge Network has built a nice page for all your test network and faucet needs [here](https://www.bridgenetwork.com/testnetguide).\\n\\nI recommend adding the Rinkeby testnet and getting the testnet $ETH tokens as not all networks are working properly in the testnet.\\n\\n**Step 1:**\\n\\nThere are two missions for the testnet but we only need to complete the first mission. The airdrop will be the same regardless of the number of missions you completed.\\n\\nGo to <https://testnet.bridgenetwork.com/> and connect your wallet.\\n\\nUnder “Token Bridge”, choose your token (from the faucet before), network from (your current network), network to, amount and receiving address (your own address). Confirm your transfer.\\n\\n**Step 2:**\\n\\nFill in the [form](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdBdDOyTpjLJu_vu4jNnQdB8suiyC0hPZo0vPTQRqKFNotiTA/viewform?usp=sf_link) to register your submission. That’s all for the testnet.\",\"timestamp\":1640571346,\"title\":\"Airdrop Guide — Bridge Network\"},\"digest\":\"3OnOaZW48ey3zzzVaLrZyCHkwK2kkFzFxyoVIse3aUk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x78A60DBDbb8f80837fc910fC8f0BB2235Ec2b6aA\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MXT855ulGG60jk6WHddQQt70LD6R0GutH4xinjVvxqc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7pCWRWQTLmTMzUHKlaQDUjEXUfQVhBa54JVdIcF0hEA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"tQ5bfu4COX4hHd9Fiypzorkz5rbXVp2CW8ttPwN1NUFFchKZmt1moBChcd-iGugV8aHEXbBoAQWwhlGUpwh4Kw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x710b5adeb10c705b3510af31f4529f786096a59e641a077e05e36d8cf8e24f1e29414cdb527c608099cad8f94249bc0a2159d66c357a1a4bed703c79cce510b91c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"MXT855ulGG60jk6WHddQQt70LD6R0GutH4xinjVvxqc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"7pCWRWQTLmTMzUHKlaQDUjEXUfQVhBa54JVdIcF0hEA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"3OnOaZW48ey3zzzVaLrZyCHkwK2kkFzFxyoVIse3aUk\"}"